Provide examples in the following man-pages:

ifdstreambuf.yo
milter.yo
ofdstreambuf.yo

For changelog:

  * New class: FoldStreambuf, std::streambuf specialization folding long lines
               to lines of a configurable right margin (cf man -e bobcat 
               foldstreambuf)

  * New class: FoldStream, wrapper class around FoldStreambuf (cf man -e bobcat
               foldstream) 

  * New class: lmargin, to act as manipulator with FoldStreams or
               FoldStreambufs modifying the left margin (number of indented
               blanks) (cf. man -e bobcat lmargin)


